China shuts down over 3,900 illegal websites.
By K J M Varma Beijing, Jul 23 (PTI) A total of 3,918 illegal websites were shut down by Chinas Internet watchdogs from April to June this year, official media reported today. The websites included those that published content that jeopardised national security, and those that spread violence, vulgarity or ungrounded rumours, according to the statement by the Cyberspace Administration of China (CAC) issued last night. 